---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageMeta from '@/components/PageMeta.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Strategy"
  description="UK Industrial Strategy context, Smart Data Scheme sequencing, OPDA programme phases, and the project roadmap."
>
<PageMeta category="Section overview" variant="brand" updated="Updated 2026-05-14" />

      <h1>Strategy</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        What this programme is meant to achieve, the wider government strategy it sits
        inside, the phasing OPDA has committed to, and the live project roadmap. Useful
        for new joiners, funders and stakeholders who need the elevator pitch and the
        2–3 year arc in one place.
      </p>

      <h2 id="plans">Plans</h2>
      <p>OPDA's own roadmap and the published programme phases.</p>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <a class="card" href="/strategy/strategy-overview">
          <div class="pill pill--brand">Start here</div>
          <h3>Strategy overview</h3>
          <p>Why OPDA exists, what it intends to deliver, and how it measures progress.</p>
        </a>
        <a class="card" href="/strategy/project-roadmap">
          <div class="pill pill--info">Built</div>
          <h3>Project roadmap</h3>
          <p>The live cross-workstream roadmap — Sandbox cohort, conformance work, semantic-model phases.</p>
        </a>
        <a class="card" href="/strategy/programme-phases">
          <div class="pill pill--info">Built</div>
          <h3>Programme phases</h3>
          <p>Sandbox → Live trust framework → National rollout. Mirrors the Open Banking sequence.</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <h2 id="wider-context">Wider context</h2>
      <p>The government strategy that authorises and shapes the work.</p>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <a class="card" href="/strategy/industrial-strategy">
          <div class="pill pill--info">Built</div>
          <h3>UK Industrial Strategy &amp; Smart Data</h3>
          <p>Property as a priority Smart Data sector. DMCC Act 2024 → DSIT Smart Data scheme → property sandbox.</p>
        </a>
        <a class="card" href="/strategy/mhclg-roadmap">
          <div class="pill pill--info">New</div>
          <h3>MHCLG Home Buying and Selling Reform Roadmap</h3>
          <p>The government's plan to make buying and selling a home quicker, cheaper and less stressful — the most authoritative current anchor for the initiative.</p>
        </a>
        <a class="card" href="/governance/strategic-alignment">
          <div class="pill pill--info">Built</div>
          <h3>Strategic alignment (HMLR · DSIT · DVSTF)</h3>
          <p>Existing alignment with HMLR strategy, DSIT National Data Strategy, DVSTF, W3C VC, and the Trust Over IP layer model.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
</Layout>
